/target
Cargo.lock
# Proprietary map/texture content is dev-only and must never be committed
# (see DESIGN.md §11 Dust2 policy). Generated caches/paks are also ignored.
*.bsp
*.wad
*.p3dpak
*.p3dworld
*.p3dtex
*.p3dmesh
*.p3dskin
*.p3danim
# ...except intentionally-committed project-owned test/generated assets:
!examples/openstrike/assets/**/*.glb
